o their  \neventual receipt.\n The Group\u2019s policy for recognition of revenue (rental income) from leases is described in Note 2.7.1.\n 2.7 Leasing", "metadata": {"source": "/content/drive/MyDrive/pidilite/Annual-Report-2022-2023.pdf", "page": 202}, "type": "Document"}}